                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.13/26.</note>
                        <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-12-20">
                                    <hi rend="italic">December 20, 1913</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>In his message accompanying the amnesty bill the President said that he
                            vetoed it because of its provisions covering common crimes.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>.</signed>
                        </closer>
